{
  "stem": "3475.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they had us-- they gave each one of us a ration of bread for-- to go on the road.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I sewed myself up a little sac that I-- it was hanging from my neck inside my shirt.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because people would steal from another, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anybody would steal.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I don't say 'anybody,' but many people would to save their life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Incidentally, going back to Auschwitz, as I remember now-- we were talking about it before.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to-- they used to bring Jewish people from all over Europe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the characterization-- like, we talked about Jewish people from Italy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had it the hardest over there because they were completely unused to the hardships.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the second group of Jews that had it very bad were the Dutch Jews from Holland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were all very well educated, very refined people, very nice people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Unfortunately, there was no demand there for refined and nice people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was dog-eat-dog, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they didn't last very well, either.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then the, the Hungarian Jews came in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Hungarian Jews only spoke Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They didn't speak any Jewish at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Consequently, they didn't make any friends with the other Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And myself, I learned to speak Yiddish in the labor camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And as I stayed on longer and longer, my-- I perfected my Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because you had to, to get along with people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so that's what I wanted to bring up-- it came to my mind, you know, how different Jewish people from different parts of Europe were better equipped for this hard, hard life.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Ourselves, being from Poland, we always had hardship from the Polacks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we were used, a little better, to the hard life.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
